/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781087832/chitratech-shop/seed/collection_05.jpg","title":"Modern Classic"}],"categories":[{"id":"cami","name":"Cami","image":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781103136/chitratech-shop/seed/category_cami.jpg","linkHref":"/main-product?category=Cami","stock":14,"order":3},{"id":"knitwear","image":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781103135/chitratech-shop/seed/category_knitwear.jpg","name":"Knitwear","linkHref":"/main-product?category=Knitwear","stock":72,"order":2},{"id":"polo","stock":52,"linkHref":"/main-product?category=Polo","order":4,"image":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781103138/chitratech-shop/seed/category_polo.jpg","name":"Polo"},{"id":"t-shirt","name":"T-Shirt","image":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781103134/chitratech-shop/seed/category_tshirt.jpg","order":1,"linkHref":"/main-product?category=T-Shirt","stock":120}],"testimonials":[{"id":"1","avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781428964/chitratech-shop/testimonials/f0yk5tr9i0tnhmefk3b5.jpg","rating":4.9,"name":"Mina Gurung","date":"2 days ago","text":"The fit feels very flattering and the pieces are easy to mix and match with other items in my wardrobe. Quality that truly lasts."},{"id":"2","text":"The fit feels considered, like it was tailored without the tailor. Minimal branding, maximum quality. Exactly what I wanted.","name":"Jenish Shrestha","date":"1 week ago","rating":4.9,"avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781434299/chitratech-shop/testimonials/wnf8dukaoaakznlohnyu.webp"},{"id":"3","rating":4.9,"avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781429135/chitratech-shop/testimonials/efvsr9bsppyxzzoukno6.jpg","date":"2 weeks ago","text":"I now own three pairs of the trousers. That says everything. The fabric comfort is unmatched in this price range.","name":"Messi"},{"id":"4","name":"Karina","date":"3 weeks ago","text":"The fit feels very flattering and the pieces are easy to mix and match with other items in my wardrobe.","avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781429116/chitratech-shop/testimonials/wvsd3nil2f0ns1ap3lbi.jpg","rating":4.9},{"id":"5","rating":4.8,"avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781428919/chitratech-shop/testimonials/hor7f8etiqunk3gc1q8l.jpg","name":"Bhuwan","text":"The jacket feels modern without being overdone. I can wear it for a smart look during the week and still style it casually on weekends.","date":"1 month ago"},{"id":"6","date":"1 month ago","name":"Wonyoung ","text":"Every piece feels intentional. The fabric, color, and fit make simple outfits look much more polished.","avatar":"https://preview.redd.it/240109-jang-wonyoung-instagram-update-v0-1by307c1xdbc1.jpg?width=1080&crop=smart&auto=webp&s=ee8860eec92f5f578f5b21baad1974370e8dbf9a","rating":4.9}]}}]
